8b3c3f5b6ca3","tid":364852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"習仲勛在毛時代被折磨得神經失常是假，其實他一直很清醒，裝瘋賣傻只是為了保護自己的家人不受株連。習近平後來被平反後，被委以重任，而他主管廣東，和廣東華人華僑接觸比較多，從他們那裡才真正了解到西方的真實生活，尤其是政治狀態與政治制度，這是習仲勛政治思想轉變的關鍵。從那時起他就要求子女們有機會的時候都&ldquo;遠走高飛&rdquo;，他說，報效祖國也可以到國外去，但留在國內，說不定就會某一天受到政治迫害，更不用說報效祖國了。但他要求子女中留一個搞政治的，而且希望是那個最淳樸沒有心機的習近平，他說，在中國這種政治下，別以為有心機就能夠成功，張春橋、江青有心機吧，滅亡得更快。習仲勛自己一直對當局與毛澤東直言不諱，在政治上從來不參與迫害人，表現得毫無心機，雖然受到了迫害，但屬於最終笑到最後的人。"},{"pid":"0ecb06ed89e93ac28409e46beed6e62010f11b7c","tid":364852,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CC8dGY9VAAA1Bxk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCC8dGY9VAAA1Bxk.jpg&h=0bee2fe1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n求seed</blockquote><br />\n呢個都唔係</blockquote><br />\n呢位好似係葉劍英元帥孫女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得咁靚 唔似雜種"},{"pid":"99c77773707531725e372947a2688b36fb43612e","tid":364852,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"五毛呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19d3180369145639dd7cb31ba305d6f5353222c","tid":364852,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"佢有其他相，豬好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d530baadbd5b41d5dae7f5d6b5a3d7553b438132","tid":364852,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/141912_599fc171821b8daaad111c7050d4efde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2